      .col-sm-4
        h2 #{mediaAmount} Uploads &nbsp
          i.fa.fa-upload
        p The amount of  times users have
        | chosen us for hosting their media
      .col-sm-4
        h2 #{viewAmount} Views &nbsp
          i.fa.fa-users
